4 5. "Court holding facility" means a secure facility, other than an adult correctional facility
5 or adult lockup, used to temporarily detain individuals before or after a detention
6 hearing or other court proceedings, and is not used to detain individuals overnight.
7 6. "Individual justice planning" means a process to identify, accommodate, and develop
